@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_dokcki(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = wp.sin(tmp)
    tmp = (((tmp + 0.71 * tmp + 0.08) / (v0 + 0.17 / v1 + 0.91)) / ((v1 + 0.34 * v1 + 0.22) * v2))
    v2 = v0
    v1 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.05 + v1 + 0.19)) * ((v2 + 0.64 - v0 + 0.79) * (v2 + 0.81 / v1 + 0.92)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((v0 + 0.75 - v0 + 0.14) * wp.sin(v0 + 0.64)))
    tmp = (v0 / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.01) * tmp))
    v0 = ((wp.exp(tmp + 0.13) / wp.sin(v1 + 0.08)) + 0.16)
    data[tid] = v0
